Author: edennottheproject
Content:
I'm posting all tarot readings here so members can refer to their readings easier.

If you want me to do your reading, PLEASE TAG ME and come with a question if you want to, otherwise it's general advice for the month/time period

Your options are:
- 3 cards - Past Self, Current Self, Advice for the Future
- 6 Cards - Your Obstacle, Your Inner Wisdom, Your Strengths, Mindset to Take, Actions to Take, Will I Succeed? 
- any other 3-5 card combination
- Any more than that is on special request and time and if I have the energy for it

I will only do your reading if you are willing to be in a voice channel - aka kocok kartu barengan like 2/3 other people. otherwise it will not hit the same
THIS IS NOT DIVINATION.
Yes, I am using ChatGPT to help me interpret because i cannot google all the meanings of the cards that quickly
